nk\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-linked\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\"}, {\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"score\": 0.5566448979703846, \"rank\": 0.7964580867617329, \"text\": \"Islamist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\"}, {\"begin\": 400, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"score\": 0.9965712144984205, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-K\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The academic study of 27 ISIS-linked attacks or disrupted plots since October revealed that of the 58 suspects, 38 were aged between 13 and 19, according to Peter Neumann, professor of Security Studies at King's College London.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-linked\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\"}, {\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_R._Neumann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3107543604687074e-13, \"text\": \"Peter Neumann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_R._Neumann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_R._Neumann\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_of_Romania\", \"score\": 0.999939032757109, \"rank\": 6.071503070562749e-05, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_of_Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_of_Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999998967041446, \"rank\": 1.0327811789743341e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CNN was also able to verify most of Neumann's data with European security officials.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.609199275043042e-16, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}, {\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"score\": 0.9999890367754023, \"rank\": 1.0955010462241173e-05, \"text\": \"Neumann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neumann noted the latest Europol data showed \\\"the number of attacks and planned attacks has more than quadrupled\\\" since 2022.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"score\": 0.9999890367754023, \"rank\": 1.0955010462241173e-05, \"text\": \"Neumann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Europol\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europol\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The apparent uptick in the recruitment of young radicals to carry out acts of terror comes as European security officials express worries at a potential resurgence of organized - or \\\"directed\\\" - terror attacks.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Summer Olympics in Paris, which start on Friday, have been specifically threatened by ISIS-K, the Islamic State in Khorasan,\\u00a0an\\u00a0active\\u00a0ISIS affiliate stemming from Central Asia.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.7760588457311526e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"score\": 0.9965712144984205, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-K\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7680190155856875e-31, \"text\": \"Islamic State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\"}, {\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khorasan_province\", \"score\": 0.6998015896142233, \"rank\": 0.4289742462144979, \"text\": \"Khorasan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khorasan_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khorasan_province\"}, {\"begin\": 1199, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.426204568153648e-70, \"text\": \"ISIS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group has built a remarkable presence in Turkey over the past three years, according to court documents and analysts.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4358608539903533e-17, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023 alone, 426 ISIS-K suspects were detained in 122 operations, according to Turkey's MIT intelligence agency.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"score\": 0.9965712144984205, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-K\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4358608539903533e-17, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Intelligence_Organization\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.04856244576896e-27, \"text\": \"MIT\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Intelligence_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Intelligence_Organization\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A UK security source said the so-called \\\"directed terror threat\\\" had become a greater concern over the past 18 months, with ISIS-K the most potent group under scrutiny.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999527063, \"rank\": 4.595353701462634e-11, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"score\": 0.9965712144984205, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-K\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Young people accessing extremist spaces and media online also continues to be a significant issue, the source said.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Groups like (ISIS-K are) specifically targeting young teenagers,\\\" Neumann said.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"score\": 0.9999890367754023, \"rank\": 1.0955010462241173e-05, \"text\": \"Neumann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They may not be very useful.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They may mess up.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They may change their mind,\\\" he said, but they are \\\"not least less suspicious.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who would think of a 13-year-old as a terrorist?\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One is enough.\\\"\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Neumann added that teenagers were being recruited through\\u00a0social media platforms like TikTok, dragged through algorithms into \\\"bubbles\\\" online where jihadist recruiters can reach them.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"score\": 0.9999890367754023, \"rank\": 1.0955010462241173e-05, \"text\": \"Neumann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georg_Neumann\"}, {\"begin\": 2126, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.105640432737411e-40, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 2189, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 0.9999999728834158, \"rank\": 2.704927764571369e-08, \"text\": \"jihadist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(ISIS-K) is by far the most ambitious and aggressive part of ISIS right now,\\\"\\u00a0he said, adding this meant the group could plan larger, more complex plots with several attackers, at the same time as doing \\\"lots of people fishing for people on the internet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2228, \"end\": 2234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"score\": 0.9965712144984205, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-K\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 2288, \"end\": 2292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.42620456815364